= HELP ME, HACKERS!

http://help-me-hackers.com/

== INSTALLATION

=== UNIX, Mac OS X

    $ gem update --system # gem ~> 1.3.6
    $ gem install bundler
    $ git clone http://github.com/komagata/help-me-hackers.git
    $ cd help-me-hackers
    $ cp config/twitter_auth.example.yml config/twitter_auth.yml
    $ bundle install
    $ rake db:migrate
    $ rake db:seed
    $ ./script/server

Access to http://localhost:3000/

=== Windows

    > COPY vendor\win32\sqlite3\sqlite3.dll c:\WINDOWS\system32\
